Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}I look across a raging war and feel the steady beating of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}嵐の前の靜けさに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}刃を振り下ろしていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:12.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}繰り返しa memory fading 今も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:17.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}時代を超えてI tell a story響く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:22.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣戦布告の詩 残酷に染もる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}この誓いを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}We'll fight until the bitter end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}途切れた息の根を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}汚れた世界を繋ぎ止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}僕らの歯車を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}it's time to Stop & Rewind(Stop & Rewind)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}失った冀望を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}壞れた時間のピースを集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}取り戻す為に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}you need to Fall & Unwind(Fall & Unwind)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}走り出す鼓動さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}限りない慈しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}導き出すアルペジオ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}A Savior of Song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我望向激烈的战场 感受我心脏不断的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}迎着暴风雨前的寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}手起刀落斩开平淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:12.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}反反复复的记忆也已褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:17.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}慢慢讲述超越时空的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:22.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}宣战之歌已染上残酷的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这份誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们要血战到底直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}将骤然停止的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与这污秽的世界相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}我们身上滚动的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}是时候令其倒回重来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}找回失去的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}收集破碎的时间断片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}为了去取回失去之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}你只需跟从脚步放下包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}充斥迈向前方的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}与无边无际的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}演奏出美丽的琶音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}救歌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be5}这是救歌之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一つ 一つ 噛み締めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}キミとの会話と記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:18.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}二つ 三つ と重ねてく言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}なんてヘンなの？感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:25.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}とても眩しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}だけど切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}青く澄み切った水のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}All I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}なんでもないこと世界が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:42.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}今 愛の意味求めている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:48.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}強い風に胸は震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}All I see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:54.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}紛れも無くこの心が選ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:58.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}ルートを真実と呼ぶなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}あの未来は多分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:04.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}ほらまた 愛で満たされる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一点一点地品味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}与你的聊天与记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:18.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}三言两语 交织在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}这是多么奇怪 所谓感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:25.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}它是那么的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}却又却悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就像青蓝澄澈的水面一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:39.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}这空无一物的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:42.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}正渴求着爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:48.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}胸膛因强风而颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:54.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}毫无疑问心灵所选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:58.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}这条道路若能被称作真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}那样的未来大概
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:04.71,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}看吧 将被爱充满
